name: And You're Almost Realized It Again
description:
"It's Like A Strange Awakening In The Night" series

This series contains three minimalist / noir jazz / ambient nocturnes in a trippy and surrealistic atmosphere. 
It's about something we all know and it's hard to explain.

Recorded on electric guitar, pedals, amps.
